      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CHUTZPAH (1) missed the frame and safely held latest finishing 6th at The Gardens following on from a win (22.84) at this track the start prior. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. Has ability and is a key runner. BRING ON BLING (7) had been racing in honest fashion recording three placings in a row before finishing fifth (23.21) at The Gardens latest. Solid record here at the distance winning four races. A forward showing wouldn't surprise. LONG DARK ROAD (2) boasts a consistent overall record including five wins from 12 starts, but missed the frame latest when fourth (23.31) over 400m at Dubbo. Has a strong record at this journey including three wins. Super consistent and can feature with the right run. MY HARLEY (8) should be thereabouts despite an unplaced run here most recently.",
